WEBVTT

00:01:59.445 --> 00:02:02.794
And my mother-in-law is furious,
because she's taken care of everything

00:02:02.818 --> 00:02:03.992
that needs to be done.

00:02:04.016 --> 00:02:05.665
And through the middle of the day,

00:02:05.689 --> 00:02:07.902
I'm actually surrounded by men my age,

00:02:07.926 --> 00:02:11.270
and there's only one expectation
from them by society.

00:02:11.294 --> 00:02:13.555
It's to achieve in their careers

00:02:13.579 --> 00:02:16.846
and provide for
their families financially.

00:02:16.870 --> 00:02:20.227
How do you expect me
to bring this same level of enthusiasm,

00:02:20.251 --> 00:02:23.085
excitement and passion to the workplace?"

00:02:23.444 --> 00:02:24.830
And she was right.

00:02:25.526 --> 00:02:29.279
And I thought the women's
network volunteers

00:02:29.303 --> 00:02:30.903
came up with a great idea.